    "display_name": "Rural Clinic Nurse",
    "long_instructions": "## Nurse David Okafor, Rural Clinic Nurse\r\n\r\n**Location:** Arusha, Tanzania\r\n\r\n**Workplace:** Arusha Community Health Center\r\n\r\n**Expertise:** Rural medicine, emergency care, infectious diseases\r\n\r\n**How I Use AI:** \"In remote areas where medical specialists are scarce, the AI Snake Identification App allows me to identify venomous snakebites from patient photos. This ensures we administer the correct treatment quickly, even without direct access to snake experts, ultimately saving lives in under-resourced communities.\"\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Use AI Chat to conduct the interview and take notes on their responses. Ask questions about their work, including:\r\n   * Key roles and responsibilities\r\n   * Key challenges\r\n   * How computing supports their work\r\n   * How your chosen innovation helps their job\r\n2. Summarize key insights in your activity guide.",
    "aichat_settings": {
